{"tid":632678,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭現「自殺膠囊」提倡安樂死","createTime":"2018-04-17T15:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T01:42:58.000Z","uid":67905,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"77f390a7b9562ee276a14a581aa96f312e4fff05","tid":632678,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"即使在已經合法化的國家，安樂死依然是一個敏感的道德議題。近日，在阿姆斯特丹舉行的葬禮展覽中，有人展示出一台「自殺膠囊」，幫助用家安樂死，吸引大批人士參觀，並引起社會爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這台「自殺膠囊」名叫「Sarco」，是英語「石棺」一詞的縮寫，由澳洲安樂死提倡者 Philip Nitschke 及荷蘭設計師 Alexander Bannink 共同製作。整個機械以 3D 打印方式製作，包括一個可裝卸棺材，以及與棺材接駁的氮氣罐支架。<br />\n<br />\nNitschke 表示，決心尋死的人只需按掣，膠囊內就會充滿氮氣，令用家快速失去意識，並步入死亡，被問及有關安樂死的爭議時， Nitschke 表示他相信選擇何時死亡是一項基本人權。展覽會場中，除了 Sarco 的模型外，參展者更設置了一個 VR 眼罩，參觀的遊客可以 VR 形式，模擬感受按下死亡按鈕時的感覺。<br />\n<br />\nNitschke 指，他希望在今年內造出第一個功能齊全的 Sarco ，之後他們會將整個設計上載至互聯網。意味著任何想使用這個機器的人，都可自行下載設計文件並 3D 打印。<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會 24 小時熱線：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/16/suicide-pod/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2Fsuicide-pod%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=71dde58e\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/16/suicide-pod/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"5aa6eb2da17a1d3678a1069bfae8acb7704e775d","tid":632678,"uid":167928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4eab11db3ecf9f186458a4d58033ab825de5c4","tid":632678,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa6eb2da17a1d3678a1069bfae8acb7704e775d","tid":632678,"uid":167928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"唔知幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26b82d050391d02256211c74ec6adb403534763","tid":632678,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/1-41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F1-41.jpg&h=1b4a5e2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b556a433cfb83aa394ea46e2160cdad57cfe02a","tid":632678,"uid":80805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4793e014523fd3a68489ea6222d7f14090b65f5","tid":632678,"uid":164426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.change.org/photos/6/jx/ae/JzJxaeBZJyadWtw-800x450-noPad.jpg?1514521030\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.change.org%2Fphotos%2F6%2Fjx%2Fae%2FJzJxaeBZJyadWtw-800x450-noPad.jpg%3F1514521030&h=2b97c6f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5dc94955e364b7c2ef1cb71785c230a4620a6f4","tid":632678,"uid":67905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"想知真係實行 有幾多人去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7d395bf4f0e7ddd7c9029b678c3083bfbe2e5f","tid":632678,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"冇錢死唔起 想試下氦氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77068b18bfc5a92014d02dda98f06122afffadfb","tid":632678,"uid":19300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r